{"id":463200,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":1,"day":31}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"918","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我们是英雄的人民","ftitle":"——纪录片《全国人民的心愿——人大三届首次会议》观后","authors":["谢其规"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热浪滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树密花盛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，红旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少战斗的人群?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少骏马在驰骋?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，机床边、田野上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们洒下了多少热汗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风里，阳光中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传出了多少喜讯?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，轧钢机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐出赤色的钢龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤色的钢龙呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前奔，向前奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刹时，大桥飞架南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂房耸向天庭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万吨水压机呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身披阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满怀豪情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立着，似顶天的巨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根根支撑新世界的梁栋呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要在我们手中诞生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而在大庆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锋利的钻头有志气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深地钻入地心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油呵，被红旗一招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象长河滚滚流不尽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击垮了一切反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"企图扼死中国的野心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听呵听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声霹雳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个世界震惊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国第一颗原子弹爆炸了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至白宫也来不及看清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发生了什么事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那蘑菇状的烟云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已宣告核垄断的妄想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为灰烬!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少个大寨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤砸碎千块顽石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梯田垒入云层……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是抗旱的坚强堡垒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万社员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结成了抗涝的钢铁长城……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有过硬的本领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举枪弹中靶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥刀，倒下多少“敌人”!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银燕，守护着祖国神圣的领空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鹰，察看着海上的每丝波纹……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵呵，千种万种困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都踩在我们脚下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天公，要听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民的命令!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，大地识英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们献出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千座银山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万担黄金……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的人民!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们前进的指针；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席手一指呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军万马冲上阵!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无往而不胜!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，站着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是苍松翠柏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹根不动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪打腰不弯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，干起活来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十万大山都摇撼!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，高举三面红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上山，敢拔老虎牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下海，敢取龙王胆!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，举起自力更生的长鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让社会主义祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日行里程三千三!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，挥舞奋发图强的铁锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按照新的蓝图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打出一个新的天地来!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民的心愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人民大会堂集中体现；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严的决议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召全国人民快马向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意气风发向未来!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年的旭日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们心头升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世纪的地平线上放霞彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远按人民的意志在转；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远按人民的意志在写!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的钢钎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要在炉旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书写新捷报；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻麦呵，要在浩荡的东风中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增产再增产!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一台新造的机器呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一担增产的粮食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不会辜负"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的期待!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远向着中南海；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们前进的步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远合着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义的节拍!"}]}